{"type": "article", "id": 33143, "title": "麻纤维做成的墨镜框，看起来很特别｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-10-10T23:16:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 33781, "name": "Shiro Studio"}, {"id": 33782, "name": "Hemp Eyewear"}, {"id": 33783, "name": "大器创意"}, {"id": 19193, "name": "Katerina Kopytina"}, {"id": 33784, "name": "Giuseppe Burgio"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 124, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161010211132s2BGb3aAwdPOQgmk.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Uluru by Shiro Studio</h3><p>在你眼中，公共场合摆放什么样的长椅会让你忍不住停下脚步？伦敦设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.shiro-studio.com/studio.php\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shiro</a> 最近为意大利品牌 <a href=\"http://metalco.it/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Metalco</a> 设计了一套打破人们固有印象的模块化长椅 <a href=\"http://www.shiro-studio.com/uluru.php\" rel=\"nofollow\">Uluru</a> 或许会让你眼前一亮。当这些利用超高性能混凝土（UHPC）制作而成的部分组合在一起后，柔和连绵的凸起不仅提供了舒适的支撑，也使得整张椅子看上去就像是一件雕塑作品。除了来小憩之外，这样的长椅也是孩子的游乐园，供他们尝试不同的位置和坐姿。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193503UHa8QK27oXMSERPZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016101019350375oLevc6fWTMDjSd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193504GscvTrUQRn8LgPh3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193504jVXu38B1EPnMKtfd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193504WcamJ97sNdIUMP6l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193503WMCPmvJc4an2lFeH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>MUG+ by DAQI CONCEPT</h3><p>如果你收集了不少马克杯在考虑该怎么更好地利用它们的话，来自台湾<a href=\"http://www.daqiconcept.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">大器创意有限公司</a>的 MUG+ 给你提供了一个让杯子大变身的机会。MUG+ 本身是一个有蓝牙功能的扬声器，只要放在容器上就可以把它变成音响。大器希望通过这个小玩意儿把“音响的选择权”交到用户手中。除了大大提高便携性之外，MUG＋ 还能因为容器的大小和材质展现出截然不同的音效，相当于你可以自己探索什么样的容器更适合某首乐曲。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/597857356/mug-turn-your-ordinary-mug-into-a-ceramics-speaker\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 35 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193431gWfn3bljT0Qs4xJm.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.735294\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193432Bq3wGaW8dzhlnCIM.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193430KMZi5kFR2dLJghWe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.545588\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610101934321NZsAqV9LwhjfKSC.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.027941\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193430JIsourmD39lXOVv7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193431oVdQREvS49uxYPly.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.864706\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Antitesi lamp by Alessandro Dadone &amp; Luca Mazzon</h3><p>          </p><p>来自米兰的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/AlessandroDadone\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alessandro Dadone</a> 和 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/luca_mazzon\" rel=\"nofollow\">Luca Mazzon</a> 两位设计师以宇宙为主题设计了这款有点特殊的灯饰，<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/42762991/Antitesi-lamp\" rel=\"nofollow\">Antitesi</a> 在意大利语中意为对照，很恰当地形容了它本身独特的结构：只有一个圆点型的光源和一块圆形二向色滤光片。这个奇特的构思源于人们看待宇宙时不同的态度，有些人会从科学角度分析，有的人则通过宗教视其为一个神秘的领域——Dadone 和 Mazzon 希望通过一个装置将两种角度融合在一起。光源点亮之后，滤光片本身会发出暖色的光芒，同时后方的墙面会被映射出一个漂亮的大光圈——当你从不同的角度观察时会发现颜色的微妙变化，滤光片上的纹路更是增添了一种迷离的效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193206vOj9ElZIMVYdkmaR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610101932069usFl6zROph0xViB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193206rn7mNyk5MXGz6UY4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193206EmkV73icYoWp65ns.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193205rLomK2sxeE84jqXl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Hemp Eyewear by Sam Whitten</h3><p>          </p><p>如果你想在墨镜的材质上换个花样，由 Sam Whitten 创立的 Hemp Eyewear 或许是一个不错的选择。那些乍看会让人误以为是木制的镜框实际上是用麻制成的，这个来自爱丁堡的品牌同时采用传统以及现代工艺对麻纤维进行加工，为人们提供了塑料和金属之外的另一种选择。就像木纹一样，由于麻纤维独特的属性，没有一副镜框是完全相同的。目前 Hemp Eyewear 有三款墨镜可选，你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.hempeyewear.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>购买，售价从 85 英镑起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010203425uSe7D25F86GfPmxB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010203425kAqXDhC34YzgVGNl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010203425AEpgkJ23nLv45KT1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010203425KZbvH3h1Su5kxiIW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010203426ZpsEP291CmVj0ISR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010203426fgD8pzVGiJEa56YP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>JOIN workstation by Giuseppe Burgio</h3><p>          </p><p>越来越多的设计师开始青睐灵活性高的模块型家具，意大利设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/bigtricks\" rel=\"nofollow\">Giuseppe Burgio</a> 也不例外，这个名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/43381033/JOIN-workstation-billion-combinations-only-3-shapes\" rel=\"nofollow\">JOIN</a> 的工作站就是他的作品。它由三种不同颜色的金属组件构成，简洁清爽的外观赋予了它很大的运用空间，人们可以随意地调整布局，组装和运输也相当方便。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193233c6wONYJLaq1GvVyx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193233JASj8rzaZbI1fTC2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193234woYG6TRyL9clxqbC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193235asI4mh9DbW5zVteq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610101932368MgHshZC4wtRKvLW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193236z29EMZHgyUchrJuf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>One by Katerina Kopytina</h3><p>          </p><p>在设计移动电源这件事上，俄罗斯设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/KaterinaKopytina\" rel=\"nofollow\">Katerina Kopytina</a> 想的不只是让它们变得更小更轻，让人们不必像是带着一块砖头那样出门，赏心悦目且不张扬的外观也是她的目标。她设计的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/42041377/One\" rel=\"nofollow\">One</a> 移动电源不仅做到了以上两点，还附带了传输站的功能，你不需要额外携带连接线，只要将两端分别同手机以及电脑相连即可。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193359UBtwOCpKkuXWbvET.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193359qrdxDnEZsBkS5hPK.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161010193356vA0qp3o4BYflT7HC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016101019335832lYNx01d7oCsyjT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610101934003wbOQ1V0SBKPCpIR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610101934009enrtHqIo3ufD1kK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}